short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Google Place Display conveniently displays the Place IDs of companies.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Google Place ID Sidebar add-on is primarily designed for developers to enhance their Google Search experience. It provides the convenience of displaying the Place IDs of companies you search for in the sidebar.
